# 🤖 AI Agent Chat App

A simple AI-powered chat application that allows users to start conversations, send messages, and receive intelligent responses in real time.

## ✨ Features
- AI-generated replies
- Start new chats instantly
- Conversation history sidebar
- Clean and responsive UI

## 🚀 Getting Started

```bash
git clone https://github.com/vaishnaviattani/ai-agent.git
cd ai-agent
npm install
npm start
